Vol / Page:  105
Edition:
Quote:  Flap Jacks. Three tablespoons oatmeal, 1 tablespoon flour, salt, small teaspoon baking soda. Mix dry ingredients, then moisten to a batter with buttermilk. Let stand for ten minutes in order to swell. Fry in bacon fat and serve round bacon for breakfast.
